<!--

Carrier type definitions to be used in HxLabwareEd2 during Microlab® STAR / VANTAGE multiflex carrier creation

displayName - name that will be displayed in a button in multiflex carrier type selection view; must be UNIQUE per each carrier
displayPartNumber - (optional) string value, part number that will be displayed under displayName
dimensions - main carrier base dimensions, in "x,y,z" format
imageFilePath - relative path (within Vector's Labware folder) that points to image representing carrier type
modelFilePath - relative path (within Vector's Labware folder) that points to carrier DirectX model (*.x)
sitePedestalOffsets - offsets, in "[x1,y1,z1];[x2,y2,z2];etc." format, used to represent center points for each pedestal position on a carrier
sitePedestalTypes - pedestal types, in "[pos1type1,pos1type2,pos1type3];[pos2type1];etc" format, configuration for each pedestal position on a carrier
modelOffsets - offsets, in "x,y,z" format, used for proper alignment of final 3D model around the template rectangle in the Deck Editor 
modelEdgeOffsets - offsets, in "x,y,z" format, used for proper alignment of 3D carrier base model with actual pedestal positions

-->

